Description: GIVEN I enter 2 characters into search box THEN predictive search should show up
GIVEN I search via WebID THEN I should end up in PDP of product
GIVEN I search a brand with international characters THEN I should see the proper brand in resultset
GIVEN I search a brand with special characters THEN I should see the proper brand in resultset
GIVEN I search by item name THEN I should see the item in resultset
GIVEN I add a product from PDP THEN I should see the bag item count increment
GIVEN I add a product from PDP THEN I should see the bag item count incremented on various pages
GIVEN I add a product from PDP AND remote/edit quantity THEN I should see bag count updated
GIVEN I am signed in AND I add a product from PDP AND I sign out THEN I should see bag count reset
